    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still firm and free of any wear or creasing. Mechanically, it is perfect; every system functions exactly as intended, and the engine bay is spotless. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a collector-grade example that requires zero investment or correction.",
