    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Every panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim remains in like-new condition. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and all electronic features and climate controls function exactly as they did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history and no upcoming maintenance required. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
