    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is honestly a total gem\u2014it's in absolutely pristine, showroom condition and has been babied since day one! It looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot, and it drives like a dream. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm sure you'll feel the love the second you hop behind the wheel. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
