    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with factory individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original rigidity, with all suspension bushings and dampening rates within factory tolerances. Finished in a deep, swirl-free gloss, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement and meticulous mechanical preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
