    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features original, factory-perfect paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a high-end ceramic coating; there are no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the original floor mats are pristine. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. I have a complete, chronological binder of all service records and original documentation. This vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered, offering a tight, responsive, and quiet experience that only a meticulously cared-for car can provide.",
